<p>Their product was once primarily focused around the â€œconversational marketingâ€ aspect of their chatbots but now you can see the reuse and repetition of the words â€œrevenueâ€ and â€œacceleration.â€</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="3ecd22a9-57c3-49dc-9226-36bb595f15d6" data-langcode="en">
