</article>
</div>
<p>Toast reinforces its identity as the all-in-one restaurant POS system with â€œBuilt for Restaurants.â€ The imagery includes their POS systems themselves as well as their logo. The supporting copy speaks to the functional value proposition of the product, giving users a reason to click through.</p>
<h3>Employ a consistent landing page design</h3>
<p>Continuing with the Toast example, you can see how their website and landing page echoes the sentiment in the ad:</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="51e09345-9899-41b5-ad09-ae01e6f599a4" data-langcode="en">
