<p>This messaging can be found across their digital territories, reinforcing their place as the â€œall-in-oneâ€ solution for restaurants. There are a number of point-of-sale systems available for businesses, but Toast focuses solely on <a href="/blog/ws/2015/01/14/restaurant-marketing">restaurants</a>. This is their brand. You can see the repeated use of the term restaurants in almost all of their copy:</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="e4e28d91-baf2-4363-9903-95e7d7111d6b" data-langcode="en">
