<p>In 2016 itâ€™s a must-have channel for any serious online marketer. I mean, just look at all the data on <a href="http://techcrunch.com/2016/01/27/facebook-earnings-q4-2015/">user growth and revenue</a> at Facebook.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="f3ef71cf-b7d4-4ea0-9c88-ef4a2315ec70" data-langcode="en">
