<h2>2: Make Sure Your Visuals Stand Out</h2>
<p>This should come as no surprise, but Facebook â€“ like most other contemporary advertising channels â€“ is visually driven. Clean, crisp, <a href="/blog/ws/2016/03/01/content-marketing-images">eye-catching images</a> stand out and help your brand image. Donâ€™t skimp on this. Invest in professional images that showcase your product(s).</p>
