<p>This is what youâ€™ll see after you click the callout bubble under â€œEligibleâ€:</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="76c3b842-2eea-445f-83dc-2b03596ff8b5" data-langcode="und">
