</article>
</div>
<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>
<p>Select &#8220;Pause campaigns&#8221; under &#8220;Type of rule,&#8221; then select the campaign or campaigns you want your rule to apply to:</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="a544599b-01c2-4262-a1c8-10fb75cbf412" data-langcode="und">
