</div>
<p>As Iâ€™ve chosen to have my example campaign pause at midnight, November 28, <strong>it will stay paused until I turn it back on manually or set an automated rule to turn it on</strong>. In my case, I set it to enable on December 2 at midnight (see below), at which point the campaignâ€™s regular settings will kick in.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="c3106583-4bbe-495d-805d-b56c61c9e407" data-langcode="und">
